Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋臟於心中的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便存在於相同之時空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或目睹相同之景物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存於你我內心之物\N亦絕非相同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我內心深處的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(無臉男)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:01:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清冷的月光照着你徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼樣的風景？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟於雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又將對月長嘆…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(後篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈能如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不願現出原形…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安份一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼剛剛的戲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續演下去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基於人的淵源跟因果形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當妖怪感應到人類的感情或執念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就會變成物怪\N對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說過您是來斬除物怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在就能斬除的話\N我也是十分樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是物怪的真與理…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有若缺少形的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔劍是無法拔出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻煩啊！物怪這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”乃事情的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”乃心的樣貌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若物怪不現出他的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我只得請妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細道出真與理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…一生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！拿酒來，酒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒酒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨手笨腳的媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個怪裡怪氣的傢伙\N物怪看上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討人厭真討人厭\N就是妳這種情緒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討人厭真討人厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…對物怪來說\N妳非常適合他附身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這確實很可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這可笑之事，妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺於物怪力量的下場即是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...妳還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳每天不停仰望的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片只屬於妳的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的...天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳只是...看著它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看著天空\N我就已經覺得很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...不離開這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真正殺死的人...是誰？\N閉...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正...殺死的人？\N閉...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再踏入蝴蝶小姐的內心！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想離開此地的話此地即是牢獄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想留在此地的話此地即是堡壘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡跟那裡都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一直認為此處是監牢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...為什麼不逃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟以前的我\N簡直就是一個模子印出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這樣美麗的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能嫁入武士之家的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...最喜歡母親大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了，蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是假的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲正要上演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二幕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳天生就是個美人\N這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑這個臉蛋再學點技藝的話\N母親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是出身貧寒的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能嫁入大戶人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~好孩子，真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡母親大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望讓她開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一直在忍耐嗎？\N咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜犧牲自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...心？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說這麼多次了妳還是不懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兒妳不是練好幾次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次，從頭開始\N對不起，對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妳怎麼嫁入武士之家？\N對不起，對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，再來一遍\N對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身已將她調教得\N不管何時都不會令家門蒙羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三幕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還請各位多多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把頭抬起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣拼命懇求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會害我過意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會茶道，彈琴跟花道是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚上會像蕩婦一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦，那要看大哥怎麼調教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼\N女人只要有錢還怕找不到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還請您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後務必請您多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親的願望...嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N請各位務必多多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人很早就過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俸祿也跟著停止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於失去一切的母親來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我嫁入武士之家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她的生存意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來\N我就無愧於梅澤家的代代祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳就成了\N替母親實現願望的工具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然那又是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了母親的願望\N而壓抑自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:12:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但身為工具的妳卻...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳戀愛的對象...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四幕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早點拿來不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨手笨腳的媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪裡怪氣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你幹嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老媽苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一個媳婦上吊自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會讓這種女人進門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過娶來做飯剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多點情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭~你怎麼講這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...別問了...別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再問了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐那個面具...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是物怪操控那個戴面具的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把妳束縛在那個家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“真“
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而接受了母親扭曲的愛\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致妳的心也跟著扭曲\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是被物怪纏上\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“理“
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...最喜歡母親大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人聽我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有認真練習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳能嫁入豪門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...已經很努力了\N我也會引以為傲的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很努力...很努力了\N之後再生個健康的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要我不要...\N為了得到夫家的疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要我不要啊...\N妳一定要拼個兒子出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人聽我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待啊~\N母親大人妳聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水天宮的符好像很有用呢\N母親大人聽我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人妳聽我說啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓他弟弟搶先的話\N那就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人為什麼不聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說聽我說啊...\N所以妳一定要先生出小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說...\N啊~真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽我說好不好\N好期待哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N好期待哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直跟白癡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳殺掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了他人的欲望\N我殺了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記自已面貌的...\N我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪\N殺了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現出...形來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後可以問件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無臉男為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要救我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得自已得救了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛上妳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是個無法實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的...物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早點拿來不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨手笨腳的媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪裡怪氣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你幹嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老媽苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一個媳婦上吊自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會讓這種女人進門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過娶來做飯剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多點情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭~你怎麼講這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳還在幹麻啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了...真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯\N實在是怪裡怪氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，蝴蝶\N真討人厭...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聾啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼事情都拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點用也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得她在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是怎麼教的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶，快把酒拿來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點拿來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(完)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能將那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜並活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N將是我此生無可比喻的珍愛
